# U_Request y U_Response: solo se completan en errores o modo debug.
# Considerar impacto de tamaño en HANA si se activa debug masivo.

### Campo U_Request — JSON request (solo errores/debug)
POST {{baseUrl}}/UserFieldsMD
Cookie: B1SESSION={{session}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "TableName": "@JCA_DLC_LOG",
  "Name": "Request",
  "Description": "JSON request Service Layer (solo errores/debug)",
  "Type": "db_Memo"
}

### Campo U_Response — JSON response (solo errores/debug)
POST {{baseUrl}}/UserFieldsMD
Cookie: B1SESSION={{session}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "TableName": "@JCA_DLC_LOG",
  "Name": "Response",
  "Description": "JSON response Service Layer (solo errores/debug)",
  "Type": "db_Memo"
}
